            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>beef mince</strong> to a bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Massage the meat with clean hands for 1 min (this helps the patty hold its shape whilst cooking)</p><p>Divide and shape the <strong>mince</strong> into 1 thin patty per person – this is your <strong>burger patty[ies]</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
