    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and charred</p><p>Set aside until serving, reserving the pan</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
