    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>burger patty[ies]</strong>, press down firmly with a spatula and cook for 5 min</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? You may need to do this in batches!</p><p>Flip the <strong>patty[ies]</strong> and reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for 5 min further until cooked through and charred (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
