    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>brioche bun</strong> with your <strong>cooked burger patty</strong>, a spoonful of the <strong>nacho cheese sauce</strong>, some of the <strong>tomato salsa </strong>and the <strong>quick-pickled green chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>chips </strong>to the side with any <strong>remaining tomato salsa</strong> and <strong>nacho cheese sauce</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
